Yes, you read that right. Toni Braxton is in Nigeria. The legendary American singer was in town to perform at the birthday celebration of media mogul Nduka Obaigbena.   #ToniBraxton at #NdukaObaigbena’s birthday celebration in #Lagos. Video: @latashalagos #BellaNaija bellanaija.com A post shared by  BellaNaija (@bellanaijaonline) on Jul 16, 2019 at 4:32am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js   #AdamsOshiomhole and #SegunAwolowo dancing with celebrant #NdukaObaigbena at his 60th birthday party in #Lagos. Video: @latashalagos #BellaNaija bellanaija.com A post shared by  BellaNaija (@bellanaijaonline) on Jul 16, 2019 at 4:39am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js Nduka Obaigbena, who is the founder of Thisday Newspaper, Arise News and Arise magazine, turned 60 on the 14th of July.
